Invocation Name: my reminder list
des: Frequently missing something To Do ? Looking for some one Remind You?.Use My Reminder List assistant to stay organized on things to do and have all reminders at one place. My Reminder List will not only help you to create reminders but also helps to update completed tasks and track the pending tasks To Do!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
